    "body": "This is how it would look like if we remove all the unnecessary stuff from that code.\r\n```\r\nfunc () getLogs(from, to uint64) ([]*Logs, error) {\r\n    res := []*Logs{}\r\n\r\n    batchSize := t.config.BatchSize\r\n    additiveFactor := uint64(float64(batchSize) * 0.10)\r\n\r\n    i := from\r\n\r\nSTART:\r\n    dst := min(to, i+batchSize)\r\n\r\n    logs, err := t.provider.GetLogs(i, dst, ...)\r\n    if err != nil {\r\n        if tooMuchDataRequestedError(err) {\r\n            // multiplicative decrease\r\n            batchSize = batchSize / 2\r\n            goto START\r\n        }\r\n        return nil, err\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    res = append(res, logs...)\r\n    i += batchSize + 1\r\n\r\n    // update the batchSize with additive increase\r\n    if batchSize < t.config.BatchSize {\r\n        batchSize = min(t.config.BatchSize, batchSize+additiveFactor)\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    if i <= to {\r\n        goto START\r\n    }\r\n    return logs, nil\r\n}\r\n```",
